query:
SELECT ar.id, ar.intakeId, ar.checklistKey, ar.proposedValue, ar.status, ar.sendCount, ar.lastSentAt, ar.token, ar.proposedPreviewToken, i.businessName, i.email 
FROM action_requests ar 
JOIN intakes i ON ar.intakeId = i.id 
ORDER BY ar.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 1;
